lead_paragraph: Former U.S. Secretary of State Hillary Clinton and former New York City mayor Michael R. Bloomberg have rolled out the next phase of a program that collects data to close gender gaps in  various aspects of women's lives.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Unveils New Partnerships to Close Gender Data Gaps
